ons of the proposed method, conductivity imaging\nappears to be feasible for application to the early diagnosis in the future.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Jan 2022 12:08:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 9 Jan 2022 13:17:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-11"}
