 sensitivities and expectations regarding the accurate\nrepresentation of their cultural identity and traditions, which can shape\nindividuals' preferences and inclinations toward certain visual styles,\naesthetics, and design choices. As a consequence, we think they are an ideal\ncandidate for a preliminary investigation of image culturization.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Jan 2022 12:10:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 14 Jan 2022 10:27:34 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 18 Aug 2022 21:51:13 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 6 Mar 2023 21:16:01 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Sun, 19 Mar 2023 17:42:41 GMT"},{"version":"v6","created":"Fri, 12 May 2023 14:18:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-15"}
